snippet.title: Do You Trust Your Boyfriend?　||　Killer Profile　2021　☀️💙🌸　#LMN​​ - Lifetime Movie Based On True Story
snippet.description:
Social media and the dangers of catfishing take a sinister turn when a group of friends determined to test their boyfriends’ loyalties create a profile under the fake name Heather. The girls learn their boyfriends are (mostly) loyal to them, but when the real Heather shows up at their school, they realize their harmless game will have killer consequences.

Director:　　Ted Campbell
Stars:　　 Lawson Greyson - Kendall Cato - Gina Simms
